&quot;Slide 3&quot;&gt;&lt;/button&gt;\r\n        &lt;/div&gt;\r\n        &lt;div class=&quot;carousel-inner&quot;&gt;\r\n            &lt;div class=&quot;carousel-item active&quot;&gt;\r\n                &lt;svg class=&quot;bd-placeholder-img bd-placeholder-img-lg d-block w-100&quot; width=&quot;800&quot; height=&quot;600&quot; xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&quot; role=&quot;img&quot; aria-label=&quot;Placeholder: Third slide&quot; preserveAspectRatio=&quot;xMidYMid slice&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot;&gt;\r\n                    &lt;rect width=&quot;100%&quot; height=&quot;100%&quot; fill=&quot;#81a3d2&quot;&gt;&lt;/rect&gt;\r\n                &lt;/svg&gt;\r\n                &lt;div class=&quot;carousel-caption d-none d-md-block&quot;&gt;\r\n                    &lt;h5&gt;First slide label&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n                    &lt;p&gt;Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Sint nesciunt numquam sit cumque laudantium suscipit praesentium vero, aspernatur repellat eos deserunt rem labore ipsa laboriosam ullam dolorum incidunt? Esse, labore.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n                &lt;/div&gt;\r\n            &lt;/div&gt;\r\n            &lt;div class=&quot;carousel-item&quot;&gt;\r\n                &lt;svg class=&quot;bd-placeholder-img bd-placeholder-img-lg d-block w-100&quot; width=&quot;800&quot; height=&quot;600&quot; xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&quot; role=&quot;img&quot; aria-label=&quot;Placeholder: Third slide&quot; preserveAspectRatio=&quot;xMidYMid slice&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot;&gt;\r\n                    &lt;rect width=&quot;100%&quot; height=&quot;100%&quot; fill=&quot;#79a4eb&quot;&gt;&lt;/rect&gt;\r\n                &lt;/svg&gt;\r\n                &lt;div class=&quot;carousel-caption d-none d-md-block&quot;&gt;\r\n                    &lt;h5&gt;Second slide label&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n                    &lt;p&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Sed natus illo corrupti consectetur assumenda harum mollitia n